\c 7
\p
\v 1 Zvino Erisha wakati: Inzwai shoko raJehovha ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha: Nenguva inenge ino mangwana, chiyero cheupfu hwakatsetseka hweshekeri, nezviyero zviviri zvebhari pashekeri pasuwo reSamaria.
\v 2 Zvino ishe mambo waaiva akasendama paruoko rwake wakapindura munhu waMwari ndokuti: Tarirai, \add dai\add* Jehovha akaita mahwindo kumatenga, chinhu ichi chingaitika here? Iye ndokuti: Tarira, uchaona nemeso ako, asi haungadyi zvazvo.
\p
\v 3 Zvino kwaiva nevarume vana vemaperembudzi panopinda pamukova, ndokuti umwe kune umwe: Tinogarirei pano kusvika tafa?
\v 4 Kana tikati: Tichapinda muguta, zvino nzara iri muguta, uye tichafiramo; uye kana tikagara pano, tichafawo. Naizvozvo ikozvino hendei tinowira mumusasa weVaSiriya; kana vakatirega tichirarama, tararama; kana vakatiuraya, tichafa.
\v 5 Zvino vakasimuka mambakwedza kuenda kumusasa weVaSiriya. Zvino vakati vasvika kumucheto kwemusasa weVaSamaria, zvino tarira, kwaiva kusina munhuko.
\v 6 Nokuti Jehovha waiva anzwisa hondo yeVaSiriya ruzha rwengoro, neruzha rwemabhiza, ruzha rwehondo huru; ndokuti umwe kune umwe: Tarira, mambo waIsraeri wakatihaira* madzimambo eVaHiti nemadzimambo eVaEgipita kuzotirwisa.
\v 7 Naizvozvo vakasimuka ndokutiza mambakwedza, ndokusiya matende avo nemabhiza avo, nembongoro dzavo, musasa uye musasa sezvauri, ndokutiza neupenyu hwavo.
\v 8 Zvino vemaperembudzi pavakasvika pamucheto wemusasa, vakapinda mune rimwe tende, ndokudya ndokunwa, ndokutakura kubvapo sirivheri sirivha negoridhe nenguvo, ndokuenda ndokuviga.
\v 9 Zvino vakati umwe kune umwe: Hatisi kuita zvakanaka; zuva rino izuva reshoko rakanaka, asi isu takazvinyararira. Kana tikamirira kusvika kwava kuchena kwemangwanani, murango uchatiwana. Zvino ikozvino, uyai tiudze imba yamambo.
\v 10 Zvino vakasvika ndokudanidzira kumutariri vesuwo reguta, ndokuvaudza vachiti:: Takasvika kumusasa we, zvino tarirai, kwanga kusina munhuko kana inzwi remunhu, asi mabhiza akasungirwa, nembongoro dzakasungirwa, namatende sezvaari.
\v 11 Zvino wakadana vatariri vesuwo, ivo ndokuudza imba yamambo mukati.
\p
\v 12 Zvino wakasimuka usiku ndokuti kuvaranda vake: Ndichakuudzai zvino VaSiriya zvavakatiitira. Vanoziva kuti tine nzara; naizvozvo vabuda pamusasa ndokuzvivanza musango vachiti: Kana vabuda muguta, tichavabata vari vapenyu tigopinda muguta.
\v 13 Zvino umwe wevaranda aake wakapindura ndokuti: Regai vatore mashanu emabhiza asara, asara mukati me\add guta\add* (tarirai, vakaita sechaunga chose chaIsraeri chakasara mariri; tarirai vakaita sechaunga chose chaIsraeri chakapedzwa, ngatitume tione.
\v 14 Zvino vakatora mabhiza maviri engoro, mambo ndokutuma shure kwehondo yeVaAsiriya achiti: Endai, muone.
\v 15 Zvino vakavatevera kusvika kuna Joridhani, zvino tarira, nzira yese yakazara nenguvo nemidziyo VaSiriya zvavaiva varasa pakukurumidza kwavo. Nhume ndokudzokera ndokuudza mambo.
\v 16 Zvino vanhu vakabuda, ndokupamba musasa weVaSiriya. Naizvozvo chiyero cheupfu hwakatsetseka chakava cheshekeri, nezviyero zviviri zvebhari zveeshekeri, zvichienderana neshoko raJehovha.
\p
\v 17 Zvino mambo wakaisa ishe waiva amire paruoko rwake kuva murindi wesuwo; vanhu ndokutsika nepamusoro pake pasuwo, iye ndokufa, munhu waMwari sezvaaiva ataura iye wakataura pakuburukiravakamutsikirira musuwo, akafa sezvakange zvarehwa nomunhu waMwari, wakataura shoko iro musi wakaburukira mambo kwaari.
\v 18 Zvikaitika sezvakange zvataurwa nomunhu waMwari kuna mambo, zvaakati: Mangwana nenguva ino zviyero zviviri zvebhari zvichatengeswa neshekeri, nechiyero chimwe choupfu hwakatsetseka neshekeri pasuwo reSamaria;
\v 19 mukuru uyo akapindura munhu waMwari, akati: Zvino tarira, kunyange Jehovha akaita mahwindo kudenga, chinhu ichi chakadai chingaitwa here? Iye akati Tarira, uchazviona nameso ako, asi haungazvidyi.
\v 20 Ndizvo zvaakazoitirwa; nokuti vanhu vakamutsikirira musuwo, akafa.
